fields.name: Impulse Treadmill
fields.description: This device is generally used for walking, running, or climbing while staying in the same place. The belt moves to the rear, requiring the user to walk or run at a speed matching the belt. The rate at which the belt moves is the rate of walking or running.

fields.name: At Home Rowing Machine
fields.description: The rowing machine is an excellent choice for a great cardio workout that works the entire body. It's low impact which is perfect for exercisers with joint issues. If done properly, you can get a great workout with little risk of injury.

fields.name: Nike Black Short Sleeve Shirt
fields.description: This Nike Run Breathe T-Shirt is crafted with short sleeves and a crew neck for a classic look. The top then comes featuring flat lock seams to prevent chafing and is equipped with Nike's signature DRI-FIT technology to help move sweat away from the skin fast to keep you feeling cool, dry and comfortable.

fields.name: Lower Body Thigh Machine
fields.description: Lower body Machine for storing in your home that allows you to build muscle in your Thighs & Glutes.

fields.name: Chest Press Machine
fields.description: The seated chest press machine is an upright version of the standard lying bench press machine. The arms, placed under a weight-bearing load, are pushed away from the chest and returned to starting position.

fields.name: Elliptical Cross Trainer
fields.description: The seated chest press machine is an upright version of the standard lying bench press machine. The arms, placed under a weight-bearing load, are pushed away from the chest and returned to starting position.

fields.name: 10kg Kettlebell
fields.description: The kettlebell is a cast iron or cast steel ball with a handle attached to the top (resembling a cannonball with a handle). It is used to perform many types of exercises, including ballistic exercises that combine cardiovascular, strength and flexibility training.

fields.name: B-Fit Treadmill Machine
fields.description: The Lontek x510 Bluetooth Treadmill is a space-saving and stable running machine. It is a very high-quality piece of home fitness equipment and features a powerful motor and a large joint-friendly running surface. You won’t get bored while working out thanks to the phone/tablet holder and integrated speaker.

fields.name: B-Fit Stationary Bike
fields.description: Designed for regular use in a home environment, the SB1.16 Indoor Cycle from BH Fitness offers a sturdy and smooth cycle. Built with a 16kg flywheel, friction braking system and poly-v belt transmission for a smooth, quiet and maintenance-free performance, the SB1.16 is an impressive cardio machine offering a compact footprint.

fields.name: Lat Pull Down Machine
fields.description: Multiple Adjustable Features to Ensure Muscle Isolation, Gas Sprung Adjustments, Up to 125kg Stacks, 3mm Laser Cut Steel Frames, Electro-Powder Coated in Matte Black, Laser Cut Frame Shrouds, Double, Stitched “Customisable” Pad Covers, Urethane Injection Moulded Pads
